Class PushRegistryProperties

java.lang.Object
org.springframework.boot.micrometer.metrics.autoconfigure.export.properties.PushRegistryProperties
Direct Known Subclasses:
StepRegistryProperties
@ConfigurationPropertiesSource public abstract class PushRegistryProperties extends Object
Base class for properties that configure a metrics registry that pushes aggregated metrics on a regular interval.
Since:
4.0.0
Author:
